# Repo-level environment defaults.
#
# Each workshop may also have its own workshops/<name>/.env.example.
# Copy that one to workshops/<name>/.env for the workshop's compose stack.
#
# This top-level file is for things that apply across all workshops, such as
# image tag pins shared by every stack. If a workshop overrides a variable,
# its local .env takes precedence (docker compose loads the local one).

# Pin sonda to a known-good version. Leave empty to use the published 'latest'.
# SONDA_IMAGE=ghcr.io/davidban77/sonda:v1.0.1
